quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  7,105,"Haqeequn AAala an laaqoola AAala Allahi illa alhaqqa qadji/tukum bibayyinatin min rabbikum faarsil maAAiya banee isra-eel"
  7,106,"Qala in kunta ji/ta bi-ayatinfa/ti biha in kunta mina assadiqeen"
  7,107,"Faalqa AAasahu fa-ithahiya thuAAbanun mubeen"
  7,108,"WanazaAAa yadahu fa-itha hiya baydaolinnathireen"
  7,109,"Qala almalao min qawmi firAAawnainna hatha lasahirun AAaleem"
  7,110,"Yureedu an yukhrijakum min ardikumfamatha ta/muroon"
  7,111,"Qaloo arjih waakhahu waarsilfee almada-ini hashireen"
  7,112,"Ya/tooka bikulli sahirin AAaleem"
  7,113,"Wajaa assaharatufirAAawna qaloo inna lana laajran in kunnanahnu alghalibeen"
  7,114,"Qala naAAam wa-innakum laminaalmuqarrabeen"
  7,115,"Qaloo ya moosa immaan tulqiya wa-imma an nakoona nahnu almulqeen"
  7,116,"Qala alqoo falamma alqaw saharooaAAyuna annasi wastarhaboohum wajaoobisihrin AAatheem"
  7,117,"Waawhayna ila moosaan alqi AAasaka fa-itha hiya talqafu maya/fikoon"
  7,118,"FawaqaAAa alhaqqu wabatala makanoo yaAAmaloon"
  7,119,"Faghuliboo hunalika wanqalaboosaghireen"
  7,120,"Waolqiya assaharatu sajideen"
